pullRequest.bodyText: ✅These have already been tested on Cloud Functions itself.

nodes.bodyText: You can be explicit here if you wish, though, I'd pick a bucket w/ very little else in it.
We should make sure you have an empty bucket for this if you are letting users provide the event.
If users can blindly play w/ our buckets we should talk.
There should be a WARNING: In production, you would not want to allow users the ability to provide unsanitized requests directly to APIs.
